OOC: Sheesh, about time!

::Symphony::

       Symphony turned to see Kluster.

        "Well, I've recently landed on planet Earth, and Prowl introduced me
to you Maximals, and I was wondering if I should see your leader to clarify
my Maximal status, or maybe just get some quarters and talk
to....um...what's her name," Symphony mumbles to himself,"Iron Raptor."
